<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>{{ meta.title }} &middot; Markdown source</title>
<meta name="robots" content="noindex">
<link rel="icon" href="../../assets/logo-shepherd.png">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;600&family=Source+Sans+3:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="../github-markdown.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="../source.css">
</head>
<body>
<div class="src-bar">
  <a href="../">&larr; Back to the article</a>
  <span class="src-bar__note">Rendered from <code>shepherd.md</code> in a GitHub README style</span>
  <a class="src-bar__raw" href="raw.html">View raw</a>
</div>
<article class="markdown-body">
<h1>{{ meta.title }}</h1>
<p>{% for a in meta.authors %}{{ a.name }}{% if a.equal %}*{% endif %}<sup>{{ a.affil }}</sup>{% if not loop.last %}, {% endif %}{% endfor %}<br>
{% for af in meta.affiliations %}<sup>{{ af.id }}</sup>{{ af.name }}{% if not loop.last %} &middot; {% endif %}{% endfor %}</p>
<p>{% for l in meta.links %}{% if l.url %}<a href="{{ l.url }}">{{ l.label }}</a>{% if not loop.last %} &middot; {% endif %}{% endif %}{% endfor %}</p>
<hr>
{{ body }}
</article>
</body>
</html>
